OL,3,CGeordie screenwriter hailed an
OL,4,C'absolute rockstar' after Golden Globe
OL,5,Cwin
OL,7,FA screenwriter from Gateshead
OL,8,Fcelebrated success at the 2025 Golden
OL,9,FGlobes in California, and the industry
OL,10,Fin the North East is praising his
OL,11,Fachievement.
OL,13,FPeter Straughan, who grew up on
OL,14,FTyneside, picked up Best Screenplay
OL,15,Ffor Conclave - a film about secrets
OL,16,Fand corruption within the Church as
OL,17,Fcardinals vote for a new pope.
