OL,7,FStraughan has previously had
OL,8,Fsilverware success with the BAFTA-
OL,9,Fwinning Tinker Tailor Soldier Spy, and
OL,10,Fwas nominated for an Emmy for his
OL,11,Ftelevision adaptation of Hilary
OL,12,FMantel's Booker Prize-winning novels
OL,13,FWolf Hall.
OL,15,FCloser to home, he was writer-in-
OL,16,Fresidence at Newcastle's Live Theatre
OL,17,Fand North East Screen have hailed his
OL,18,Fwork.
