OL,3,CGeordie screenwriter hailed an
OL,4,C'absolute rockstar' after Golden Globe
OL,5,Cwin
OL,7,FAlison Gwynne, Chief Executive of
OL,8,FNorth East Screen, said: "I mean
OL,9,FGolden Globes, and hearing a Geordie
OL,10,Faccent it doesn't get better than
OL,11,Fthat, does it?
OL,13,F"I stayed up to watch, I mean the fact
OL,14,Fthat he was nominated in such a
OL,15,Fstellar year was great and to see his
OL,16,Flittle face when he got up on the
OL,17,Fstage and made such a brilliant
OL,18,Fspeech, I just feel really proud.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
