OL,3,CGeordie screenwriter hailed an
OL,4,C'absolute rockstar' after Golden Globe
OL,5,Cwin
OL,7,F"I think it's really, really important
OL,8,Ffor the world to see that there is
OL,9,Fworld-class talent in the North East.
OL,10,FPeter is an absolute rockstar and
OL,11,Fwe're really excited about where he's
OL,12,Fgot to in his journey, but also it
OL,13,Fdemonstrates that there is opportunity
OL,14,Ffor emerging talent in the region to
OL,15,Freach great heights."
OL,17,FThere are big plans for the North East
OL,18,Fto make its mark in the world of
OL,19,Ftelevision and film with the Crown
OL,20,FWorks Studio development in Sunderland
OL,21,Fleading the way.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
