OL,4,C'absolute rockstar' after Golden Globe
OL,5,Cwin
OL,7,FAlison added: "We've got to do a
OL,8,Fcouple of things to grow a sustainable
OL,9,Fsector in the region. We've got to
OL,10,Fbring global production into the
OL,11,Fregion, whether that's film or
OL,12,Ftelevision, but we've also got to grow
OL,13,Four indigenous talent so we tell our
OL,14,Fown stories and we create our own IP
OL,15,F(intellectual property). Being able to
OL,16,Fsee Peter do what he's done helps both
OL,17,Fof those things."
